582ad59b/7fd17/me.jpg 175w,\n/static/c61eda952c21afa60ccd86c1582ad59b/804d2/me.jpg 350w,\n/static/c61eda952c21afa60ccd86c1582ad59b/23116/me.jpg 640w","srcWebp":"/static/c61eda952c21afa60ccd86c1582ad59b/3ba0d/me.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/c61eda952c21afa60ccd86c1582ad59b/61503/me.webp 175w,\n/static/c61eda952c21afa60ccd86c1582ad59b/850cb/me.webp 350w,\n/static/c61eda952c21afa60ccd86c1582ad59b/3ba0d/me.webp 640w","sizes":"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px"}}},"skills":["Data workflows, ETL, Airflow","Data Lakes, DWH, Delta Lake","Data Quality, Apache Spark","SQL Query, planning and Optimisation","Infrastructure instrumentation and monitoring, AWS, Kubernetes, Prometheus, Grafana","Python, Scala, Java"]},"html":"<p>Hello! I'm Arpit, a data engineer who plays with data and infrastructure.</p>\n<p>After graduation from <a href=\"http://iiitvadodara.ac.in/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">my college</a> I have joined <a href=\"https://socialcops.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">SocialCops</a> as a data engineer where I work on the data platform.\nHere's a few technologies I've been working with recently:</p>"}}]},"jobs":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Data Engineer","company":"Atlan","location":"New Delhi, IN","range":"June 2018 - Present","url":"https://atlan.com"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Built data quality as a service using <a href=\"https://spark.apache.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Spark</a> to calculate metrics such as mean, median, PII columns, outlier percentage, nulls whilst providing an interface to implement custom metrics by the user and supporting data sources like Snowflake, Data Lakes on S3, Oracle. User can also setup tests on data like <code>mean(columnA)>20</code> and service reports passed and failed checks to the user. This brought trust into the data for the user.</li>\n<li>Built an AWS deployment of open source <a href=\"https://prestosql.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Presto</a> with high available presto coordinator nodes, graceful shutdown of workers nodes to support <a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/autoscaling/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">autoscaling</a>, Cloudwatch agent to push metrics like cpu, heap usage to support monitoring and autoscaling to power ETL and interactive query workloads.</li>\n<li>Built a micro service in Java to power objects and data level authorisation like masking, column level access control for SQL queries in AWS Athena. I build this using <a href=\"https://www.antlr.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">ANTLR</a> grammar of presto and query rewrite methods.</li>\n<li>Added features like data deduplication, data ingestion from S3, running SQL queries in the workflow to Atlan Workflows</li>\n<li>Improved cataloging performance of Atlan Catalog by 90%, added versioning features such as remove a commit, rollback.</li>\n<li>{Built data pipelines using <a href=\"https://airflow.apache.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Airflow</a> for Ministry of Rural Development India's project <a href=\"https://socialcops.com/case-studies/disha-dashboard/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">DISHA</a> which includes data ingestion from third party APIs, transformation using Python/R and data sink <a href=\"https://www.elastic.co/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Elasticsearch</a> including data versioning to rollback to previous versions.</li>\n<li>Managed on-premise deployments for DISHA project, packaged the entire stack of Vue.js frontend app, Node.js backend and Airflow pipelines into debian package.</li>\n<li>Created a health monitoring service for DISHA deployment using Prometheus and Grafana to alert stakeholders of critical scenarios like failing ETL pipelines, high resource usage, high traffic on dashboard etc.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Mentor","company":"Codementor","location":"Remote","range":"Jan 2019 - Present","url":"https://codementor.io"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Provided one to one live help on given problems/bugs to mentees</li>\n<li>Taught and guided on new technologies, fields and approaches on problem-solving.</li>\n<li>Have done over <a href=\"https://www.codementor.io/arpitsolanki\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">100 sessions with 5 star rating</a> with 40+ reviews.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Data Engineering Intern","company":"SocialCops","location":"New Delhi, IN","range":"Jan 2018 - May 2018","url":"https://socialcops.com"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Built a data integration framework using celery with support for state management and incremental data ingestion.</li>\n<li>Worked with data scientists and Bussiness intelligence team to build ETL pipelines using Airflow to power analytics and dashboards</li>\n<li>Worked on building system native packages (Debian and RPM) of data integration services and ETL pipelines written in Python.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Backend Developer Intern","company":"Vstv.io","location":"Remote","range":"September 2018 - October 2018","url":null},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Worked on backend using MEAN Stack to create web services</li>\n<li>Handled audio/video streams for multiple clients per session using webRTC</li>\n<li>Integrated OAuth as auth mechanism into the platform.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Backend Developer Intern","company":"MateLabs","location":"Banglore, IN","range":"May 2017 - July 2017","url":"https://www.matelabs.ai/"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Worked on MateVerse platform integration with <a href=\"https://ifttt.com/discover\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">IFTTT</a> to run ML predictions on Google Photos, text based reviews, emails etc. It solved use cases like anomaly detection, classifying spam reviews and marketing emails etc</li>\n<li>Added OAuth, improved the internal monitoring dashboard.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Automation Tester and Code Reviewer","company":"BrainPlay","location":"Remote","range":"Feb 2017 - May 2017","url":"https://www.linkedin.com/company/brainplay-learning-solutions-llp/about/"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Worked on Database designs and optimisations with frontend and backend team.</li>\n<li>Reviewed the backend APIs for performance optmisations and robustness</li>\n<li>Wrote automated tests for APIs using Mocha and Chai</li>\n</ul>"}}]},"featured":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Human Detection and Tracking","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='255'%3e%3cpath d='M72 9h-3c-3-1-4-1-4 1h-1c0-2-3-3-3-1h-1c0-2-5-1-5 1s0 2 1 1l1-2v2h23l5 1c3 0 5 0 4-1l-1-2h-6l-3-1h-3c0-2-2-1-4 1M3 52c0 2 0 2 1 1h2c2 2 5 2 6 0h3l3 1 3-1h1l1 1h15c2 1 10 0 11-1h3l-1-1c-2-2-23-2-25-1H16c-1-1-7 0-7 1H8c-1-2-5-2-5 0m-1 55c1 2 392 2 393 0l-196-1-197 1m337 14l1 5h55v-10h-56v5M22 198v4h36v-7l-18-1H22v4' fill='%2364ffda' fill-rule='evenodd'/%3e%3c/svg%3e","aspectRatio":1.5695754716981132,"src":"/static/aef69baccc5e45028613fb18804683d7/e8606/demo.png","srcSet":"/static/aef69baccc5e45028613fb18804683d7/53aff/demo.png 175w,\n/static/aef69baccc5e45028613fb18804683d7/1844f/demo.png 350w,\n/static/aef69baccc5e45028613fb18804683d7/e8606/demo.png 700w,\n/static/aef69baccc5e45028613fb18804683d7/c9f12/demo.png 1050w,\n/static/aef69baccc5e45028613fb18804683d7/328e1/demo.png 1331w","srcWebp":"/static/aef69baccc5e45028613fb18804683d7/93ec8/demo.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/aef69baccc5e45028613fb18804683d7/61503/demo.webp 175w,\n/static/aef69baccc5e45028613fb18804683d7/850cb/demo.webp 350w,\n/static/aef69baccc5e45028613fb18804683d7/93ec8/demo.webp 700w,\n/static/aef69baccc5e45028613fb18804683d7/fbd0c/demo.webp 1050w,\n/static/aef69baccc5e45028613fb18804683d7/5c52b/demo.webp 1331w","sizes":"(max-width: 700px) 100vw,